<Turn speaker="spk1" startTime="1005.338" endTime="1050.835" fidelity="high">
<Sync time="1005.338"/>
tukaj sem danes doma. 
<Sync time="1006.949"/>
Bil sem prvorojenec in 
<Sync time="1009.247"/>
